org.gvsig.tools.util

Class PropertiesSupportHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.tools.util.PropertiesSupportHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Observable, Persistent, PropertiesSupport
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExtendedPropertiesHelper

    public class PropertiesSupportHelper
extends java.lang.Object
implements PropertiesSupport, Persistent, Observable, Cloneable
    This class is intended to serve as an aid to the implementation of PropertiesSupport. When we have a class that implements the PropertiesSupport interface, we will use PropertiesSupportHelper to implement it. For this, we will declare a property "propertiesHelper", and we will implement the interface methods delegating in it. private PropertiesSupportHelper propertiesHelper = new PropertiesSupportHelper(); ...
